                <div id="main-text">
                    
                    <p class="swing"><span contenteditable="true">3. cont</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p>
                    <p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">I said a lot there, didn't I? Boy, I'd look like an old fool if I left you two to run around town after gettign on her case, huh?</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p>
                    <p class="beat1"><span contenteditable="true">&nbsp;Tell you what. Why don't you both accompany me to my abodes, and I'll take a quick nap before we head over to that magic show of yours, Shiori?</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p>
                    <p class="beat3"><span contenteditable="true">It's not a magic show, it's a ritual! //Shiori gasps and covers her own mouth.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">That's strange. Are we being pulled into our younger selves?&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p>
                    <p class="rest1"><span contenteditable="true">Right, of course. An occult ritual, Al winked. Well, I'm sure it'll be fun whatever it is. Now come on, let's get going. I want to get at least three hours in.</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Shiori, I whisper. Are we reliving events? Are we gonna have to relive all that?</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">I don't know... Things are kind of different but kind of not. We can't <i>change</i>&nbsp;anything, of course. But... I just don't know.&nbsp; Just like last time, we're going to the seance. And I'm kind of excited about it!</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">For some reason I can't remember much about it.&nbsp; (she blocked it from her memory)</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">We're going to The Creepy Peach, Shiori whispered.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="swing"><span contenteditable="true">4. The Creepy Peach</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p>
                    <p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Now you all do what you do, while I take a quick nap so I can make sure my golden thread is nice and uncuttable when we see those soothsayers.</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Um, can we eat some cereal or something?</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">What are you kids gonna do if I told you cereal's the one thing you're not allowed to eat? he chuckled. It's on top of the fridge.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Hannah comes in. She's wearing breeches.//She's a horsegirl, Shiori whispered. //A what? //G-goodness, Shiori said, a twelve year old trying to talk like an aristocrat.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">What are you two girls doing here. Why, you two are smelling wonderful today! I can tell Santa's going to bring you lots of presents.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">"What do we smell like Miss Hannah?"<br></span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Hmm. Like cinnamon and kindness.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">That's why it's good to have children around. If only we could... add more children...</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">"Hannah's sort of thirsty," Shiori whispered to me.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">I don't know what thirsty means, actually, but I can guess. It actually makes me kind of uncomfortable. Not in a "this woman is dangerous" kind of way. More like "this woman is dangerous for whoever she ends up marrying."&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Nick comes in.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Hey! It's my two best candystore customers.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">That's what you get for opening a candy store in a place with no kids!" Shiori exclaims.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat1"><span contenteditable="true">Hell, don't I know it. But I've got a sweet tooth myself.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Nick always had this ambiguous, foreignish look to him, but he didn't have any accent. Stubble, and slightly curly hair.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Cereal for dinner? Nick frowned. He looks at Shiori. Well. That's a given. Then he looks at me. "I guess your mom's busy?</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">I just shrug at him.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Well, go ahead and just pour the milk in the sink. I'll whip up something for everybody.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Ok! Shiori says. // Go play while I cook.//Yeah sure. This is a good chance for us to look around for more snitches.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">As we leave the living room dining room, I can hear Hannah accosting Nick.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Is she sniffing him? / Have you had yourself a little amourette? The weepiest tone I've ever heard.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">First off, we're not dating, and second, no?</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Um. Let's leave them to it.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Click to Edit</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p>
